commit.message:
20040204-1.c: Don't XFAIL on sh*-*-*.

* gcc.dg/tree-ssa/20040204-1.c: Don't XFAIL on sh*-*-*.
* gcc.dg/tree-ssa/sra-12.c: Skip for sh*-*-*.

From-SVN: r220829
